    "Alphafold [25] also combined a self-distillation training with a masked multiple sequence alignment learning, leveraging unlabelled protein sequence, achieving downstream highly accurate protein structure prediction.b) Other pre-training paradigms, including CL and HL, also have been studied to capture the biology information during pre-training steps [204], [207]- [210].",
